This paper deals with Natural Language Understanding (NLU) and machine learning models for duplicate question detection, which are topics that fall under the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
